Common.LocationDescription.Common.Text: 310 is located in downtown Milwaukee's hottest neighborhood, Westown.  It is located on several MCTS bus routes with over 12 different stops within a 3-block radius. Through Milwaukee's Skywalk System, tenants are connected to over 10,000 parking spaces, 10 hotels, 5 fitness centers, the expanding Wisconsin Center, and numerous restaurants, cafes, and shops.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text: 310W is a 624,000 SF building consisting of two towers connected by an awe inspiring atrium. Located in downtown Milwaukee’s hottest neighborhood, Westown, 310W is undergoing a $30 million renovation under its new ownership, Time Equities. With suites ranging from 1,500 SF to full floors (45,000 SF) 310W can meet the needs of any tenant looking for outstanding office space in a prime location with new and plentiful amenities, abundant and easy on-site parking, walkability, and aggressive leasing packages.
